API Functionality required

File Related:
    uploadFile(file, uploadType) - HTTP/Websocket?
        file - the file to be saved
        uploadType - where to save the file. Load or Solar.
        Should return whether successful or not.

    getFiles() - HTTP/Websocket?
        Returns a list of all files saved.
        Or could pass a uploadType and get only files of that type back (Load or Solar)
        Should return a list of file names or filename id's.

